task.summary: Include damping ration and natural frequency to control generic class as parameter. Instead of use a List Comprehension to generate the time for the x axies it is used numpy linspace.

Include "icons" directory.
Implemented Internal delays in control_generic_class.py and refactored "evaluated_time_delay". Notice that now the class recognizes if there is a time delay or a internal delay.
Function get_plots not longer support a list of transfer functions as this feature will be implemented directly through the GUI.
Script "delays" was deleted from the repository as it was only a scratch. then it was remplaced by "ControlPython_GUI.py". The feedback argument is not longer evaluated in the main ( ControlPython_set_up.py ) as this process was already evaluated in control_generic_class.py.

control_generic_class.py - Include comments in the class and functions. - Set default values to the arguments. - Deleted the assignation of type to the attributes. - Deleted get_time_delay_pade as this function is not longer necessary.
ControlPython_GUI.py First script for the GUI, contains: - layouts for the main and second window. - get_window function creates second windows continuously. - include three cases for each control system type in the scope.
snake.png Inlude icon for the aplication.

control_generic_class.py - Excluded unused class arguments. - Include a "add_transfer_fuction" method to sum transfer functions in the GUI. - Refactored evaluate_time_delays.
controlpython_gui.py - Refactored
controlpython_window_gui.py - Include a new method to create a new object for each menu in the GUI.
